# Acceptance Test Procedure (ATP)

## Purpose

This document defines the Acceptance Test Procedure (ATP) for PX4-based aircraft developed under this project.

The purpose of the ATP is to verify that every aircraft meets the minimum operational, safety, and performance requirements before being released for customer use, internal deployment, or field testing.

An aircraft shall not be considered accepted until all required tests have passed.

